    "body": "Hey @iam4x! Do you remember in which cases you needed to access the container node in the connector?\r\n\r\nUsually we specify the `unmountFn` function body in the widget, where we have the knowledge of the container node and unmounts its component.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/9dcbdd582d082acaea0edeabdc7e5d6cd9173c51/src/widgets/menu/menu.js#L168-L170\r\n\r\nTo my knowledge, the connector nevers needs to access the container node because it only calls the `unmountFn` given by the widget:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/9dcbdd582d082acaea0edeabdc7e5d6cd9173c51/src/connectors/menu/connectMenu.js#L228",
